Numbers in php
    
    Operators
      +
      -
      *
      /
      %
      **
      varName++
      varName--
      varName += 25
      varName -= 25
      varName *= 25
      varName /= 25

     Math functions
       abs(value) => get the absolute value
       pow(value, pow) 
       sqrt(value) 
       max(value1, value2)
       min(value1, value2)
       round(value) => round closer value
       ceil(value) => always round up
       floor(value) => always round down
       ...
       ...
       
